item.title: Inspiration
item.description: The site that I've created wouldn't be possible without the wonderful inspiration that Leo shares on his site of similar URL naming. I sincerely hope if he ever becomes aware of my site, he'll consider it the homage that it is towards his words and sharing of experiences.
